{"tid":2496835,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] Monster Hunter Rise (48) 開場乜都要寫到明","createTime":"2021-04-20T05:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T05:55:17.000Z","uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"793d28d004f7cec3b2aee808f3a631bf52933432","tid":2496835,"uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EiH0xW3VkAYbnxc?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEiH0xW3VkAYbnxc%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=ffa537e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmhrise.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=e7fa1309\" target=\"_blank\">https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/</a><br />\n<strong>MHR混裝器</strong></p><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n4月尾2.0更新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf2L41eHSTazbXsLfoKUyQPZjKswkFMztSwuuH6Aorfq3?filename=Rsn1uM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsn1uM1.jpg&h=cab87907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月26日(五)發售<br />\nAlso available on PC(Steam 2022)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunter.com%2Frise%2Fhk%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=6d0a79f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Q&amp;A </span></span><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔同版本有咩分別？可唔可以連機？<br />\nA: 日版 港版有中文 美版冇中文<br />\nSwitch MHR冇分ser 全版本可以連機 (需要Nintendo Switch Online)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手用咩武器好？<br />\nA: 14種武器各有長短 試下打村任熟習下<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點拎特典？<br />\nA: 火芽左邊隻貓郵差&gt;新增內容<br />\n<br />\nQ : 點係地圖閃燈俾隊友睇<br />\nA : 係場地入邊禁住-號放大地圖，再禁-號<br />\n<br />\nQ : 殺完大怪之後動畫點Skip ?<br />\nA : 兩下B制<br />\n<br />\nQ : 隨從廣場點先開放?<br />\nA : 要行一次先會開到，係火芽面向個位直行到橋尾<br />\n<br />\nQ : 神火卷點拎？<br />\nA : 村5星後玩村任 村長有機會派<br />\n<br />\nQ : 海境S點出？<br />\nA : 玩交易船<br />\n<br />\nQ : 打完boss好似未完咁？<br />\nA : 要等更新！<br />\n<br />\nQ : 貓其實有咩技最好<br />\nA : 兩個技必要<br />\n- 強化咆哮 +30%會心<br />\n- cooldown時間一分鐘, 成鋪大部份時間都會發動緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 強化太鼓 x1.05倍攻, x1.2倍防<br />\n- cooldown時間90秒<br />\n<br />\nTips:<br />\n1. 有咩睇咗獵人筆記/心得先<br />\n<br />\n2. 連機嫌眼花可以熄特效<br />\n<br />\n3. 隨從廣場有棵樹可以爬上去 每次完任都有嘢可以執<br />\n（**可以儲一陣先執 唔洗每次去攞）<br />\n<br />\n4. 撳實L1左下角個小地圖可以睇到詳細地圖標記咗嘅嘢 搵礦有小小用<br />\n<br />\n5. 礦有唔少都喺啲勁高嘅地方 要用翔蟲飛嚟飛去 可以配合L1地圖去搵<br />\n<br />\n6. 船艇牡蠣 : 寒冷群島搵 / 狐火鬼燈 : 大社遺跡搵<br />\n<br />\n7. 村任2★ 上 3★要去一去隨從廣場(村右邊過橋)同寵物店老闆吹水<br />\n<br />\n8.村任打完5星 會有個特別許可任務<br />\n連續狩獵打完火龍雷狼同泥翁就可以直接打集會個hr4既首領青熊獸百龍夜行，打完直上hr4<br />\n<br />\n9. 集會所任務出發前記得食團子(即係上幾代既貓飯)<br />\n<br />\n10 : 入左場地之後，-號可以進入地圖，,再L及R睇到好多資訊<br />\n<br />\n11: 下位唔駛諗砌裝，堆高個防就夠<br />\n<br />\n12: ZL+ZR可以直接向瞄準既地方飛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n開潛艇（新農場）教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26snA%3D159411&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=ecf58ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411</a><br />\n<br />\n測試有冇中痛風 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gamewith.jp/mhrize/article/show/270133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.jp%2Fmhrize%2Farticle%2Fshow%2F270133&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=e2189f6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gamewith.jp/mhrize/article/show/270133</a><br />\n<br />\n痛風表護石List :<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14%2Fedit&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuDUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=e8c67e56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"1ed90d0792badbde0dec9877af66a11591868355","tid":2496835,"uid":201195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"今次咁快1001"},{"pid":"8487ce5637ecd5698f2da5035b6c491dbb2886ab","tid":2496835,"uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed90d0792badbde0dec9877af66a11591868355","tid":2496835,"uid":201195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:53:07.000Z","msg":"今次咁快1001"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:53:46.000Z","msg":"暗黑兵法"},{"pid":"eb3053547df8cafaf131b6709a615d0eeae2fd58","tid":2496835,"uid":201195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:54:19.000Z","msg":"Btw想問下打雷神弱特2同弱特3係咪好大分別？"},{"pid":"b2adc9a6f46872e823a04f66d221467c5ea15ffe","tid":2496835,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"想做World撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c86aad485f2e409ee65cda6c3ea5cdd2e25bb1","tid":2496835,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2adc9a6f46872e823a04f66d221467c5ea15ffe","tid":2496835,"uid":11880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:54:30.000Z","msg":"想做World撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"做"},{"pid":"330a4dacadc5efc1c4a58e4bef3501fecc6674e1","tid":2496835,"uid":4093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":